wielder of the flame of Anor.</i>

3
00:01:39,172 --> 00:01:41,889
Go back to the Shadow.

4
00:01:42,742 --> 00:01:46,418
The dark fire will not avail you,
flame of Udûn!

5
00:01:50,450 --> 00:01:54,857
You shall not pass!

6
00:02:22,183 --> 00:02:23,677
No! No!

7
00:02:24,051 --> 00:02:25,959
Gandalf!

8
00:02:33,562 --> 00:02:35,252
Fly, you fools.

9
